data.description: Horse property nestled on a sprawling 4 acre parcel. This ranch style country charmer home and property have so much to offer!  Walk up your brick walkway onto your front porch and enter through  the main door into the living room or through the side door that leads to the kitchen area.   The home has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. The master bedroom has a retreat that could be used as a craft room, office, home gym, or can become your dream closet.  There is a secondary bedroom suite with its own private bathroom.  The kitchen overlooks the family room and is perfect for entertaining with two breakfast bar seating areas and a kitchen island with pendant lighting. The family room and kitchen area share a cozy fireplace.  Step outside if you are looking for lots of space and an oasis of serenity with the most amazing views!  On the front side of the property is a well-maintained riding arena, a horse pen with a 12 x 24 shade shelter, a horse washing station and a shed for storage. Located on the back side of the property is a large fenced horse run with two additional 12x24 shade shelters. Each shade can accommodate multiple horses.  Enjoy your favorite beverage on the front porch or seating areas while watching the beautiful sunrises and sunsets. There is plenty of room for entertaining and large family gatherings creating memories to last a lifetime.  Home is connected to public water source.  Don’t miss the opportunity to make this equestrian property your own paradise!  Located in the desirable Diamond Valley area approximately one mile from the Western Sciences Academy School and Diamond Valley Lake. Short drive to wine country and the wineries!
